12
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:37,860
Bailejing?

13
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:41,290
It's located deep
in Mount Baiwan of Nanqiang.

14
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,750
Legend has it that it is an extremely

15
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,040
prosperous paradise.

16
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,830
Although Bailejing is famous,

17
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,830
the mountain is vast,

18
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:51,950
[Bailejing Research Files]

19
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:51,920
snakes, insects and poisonous ants
are very common,

20
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,250
bandits are everywhere,

21
00:04:53,250 --> 00:04:54,980
and the folks there are fierce.

22
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,600
Very few people

23
