can actually get inside.

24
00:04:58,010 --> 00:05:00,660
Mentor, you've been to Bailejing,
haven't you?

25
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:03,390
The last time I went there
was many years ago.

26
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,540
I went to Bailejing
to investigate an incident,

27
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:07,180
and I personally wrote the file.

28
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,740
We have members of the Zhang family
there in Nanqiang,

29
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:09,980
responsible for some...

30
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:11,110
intelligence work.

31
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:12,700
It's written here that

32
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,120
none of the cases there have been closed.

33
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,780
Is the situation in Bailejing

34
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:18,680
really that complicated?

35
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,830
Even you couldn't deal with it?

36
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:21,160
The key is whether you can handle it.

37
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:21,160
[Bailejing Research Report]

38
