Give it to me.

39
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:28,430
Don't get me wrong.

40
00:05:28,980 --> 00:05:30,780
I'm going there to enjoy myself.

41
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,159
Having been the Director
for so many years,

42
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,820
it's time for me to take a rest.

43
00:05:39,370 --> 00:05:40,180
By the way,

44
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:43,370
