49
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,470
Mentor,

50
00:05:51,570 --> 00:05:52,650
how about you help me recruit some people

51
00:05:52,650 --> 00:05:53,710
before you retire?

52
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,370
Figure it out yourself.

53
00:06:02,250 --> 00:06:03,430
Believe me. You can't go wrong.

54
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:03,920
Okay.

55
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:04,670
Don't worry.

56
00:06:12,770 --> 00:06:13,310
Bro.

57
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,470
It looks like you have an unusual talent.

58
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:16,770
Do you want to be a great detective?

59
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:17,570
Really?

60
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:18,780
Of course.

61
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,810
Okay.

62
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,730
We now have our first member.

63
00:06:33,570 --> 00:06:35,480
Mentor, what does this chief look like?

64
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,920
How can we find him?

65
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,600
Our chief,

66
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:39,670
Zhang Qiling—

67
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,850
