68
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,530
But wherever he went,

69
00:06:43,659 --> 00:06:45,220
he left legends about him there.

70
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:46,630
Wherever he went...

71
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,060
he left legends...

72
00:06:50,659 --> 00:06:51,830
So this chief

73
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,240
was quite the ladies' man

74
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,240
wherever he went?

75
00:06:56,370 --> 00:06:57,500
I only met this chief

76
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:59,250
a long time ago.

77
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:01,630
The chiefs are all very formidable.

78
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,870
When they act,

79
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,930
they all wear special Macabre Masks.

80
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,560
What is a Macabre Mask?

81
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,490
Macabre Masks—

82
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:10,450
it's a tradition of the Zhang family.

83
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,660
The older generation of the Zhang family,

84
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,370
when they needed to eliminate evil,

85
00:07:13,370 --> 00:07:15,420
assassinate, or launch surprise attacks,

86
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:17,750
would wear masks designed by themselves.

87
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,240
These masks,

88
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:20,540
unlike human-skin masks,

89
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:21,720
cannot be used for disguise.

90
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,330
They can only be used to cover the face

91
00:07:23,330 --> 00:07:25,060
and intimidate the opponents.

92
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:27,640
The Zhang family
really has a lot of rules.

93
00:07:27,810 --> 00:07:30,340
Is it necessary
to intimidate the opponents?

94
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:33,010
The enemies we face are all very powerful.

95
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,450
So the masks are usually made into

96
00:07:35,450 --> 00:07:38,110
the most terrifying images
in people's hearts.

97
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,020
What do you fear the most?

98
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:19,240
♪ The wind cannot disperse
the overlapping mist ♪

99
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:26,100
♪ Deep in the rainforest,
we whisper of the past ♪

100
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:31,520
♪ Holding up a lonely lamp
toward the abyss ♪

101
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:35,350
♪ Crossing wilderness,
through war fields ♪

102
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:41,340
♪ Behind us
are burning unfulfilled wishes ♪

103
